<p>The entire front panel is made of mesh which protects the front intake fans quite well. Mesh front panels also allow far more cool air in the case than a solid or glass front panel as well, which is great for those of you who care a lot about airflow.</p>

<p>On the front IO (which you can move around the case) you‚Äôll find a power/reset button, microphone/headphone jacks, two USB 3.0 ports, and two information LEDs, one for power and one for hard drive activity.</p>

<p>You can unscrew the IO from the top and mount in in two other locations on the front of the case, which is a feature I haven‚Äôt seen before myself.</p>

